industrials, the Nairobi Stock Exchange (NSE) sources said.
</P>
<P>
Kenya Breweries (KBRW.NR) dropped to 46.50 Shillings from 49
on Monday but closed a little higher at 47.75 on 503 shares.
Kenya Power &AMP; Lighting Co. (KPLA.NR) lost three Shillings to 192
on 2,600 shares, according to the NSE data.
</P>
<P>
