century.
</P>
<P>
In a message issued on the eve of "Ohi (No) Day" on Wednesday
when Athens refused an Italian ultimatum to surrender and was
dragged into World War II, Simitis said that Greeks were required
to show the same decisiveness as the generation of the 1940s.
</P>
<P>
