The statement said that South Africa commended the vision
displayed by Peru and Ecuador and welcomed the prospects inherent
in the accord of boosting bilateral trade between the two states
and attracting foreign investment to the region as a whole.
</P>
<P>
Southern Africa was moving closer to the Andean region of
Latin America, particularly in terms of economic cooperation, as
witnessed in the recent opening of South African embassies in
Lima and Caracas, the department said.  
