would be handed back to the Lesotho military later this week.
</P>
<P>
South African national newspaper Business Day quoted the
office of Botswanan President Festus Mogae as saying Tuesday that
the South African and Botswanan troops, deployed in Lesotho last
month under the auspices of the Southern African Development
Community (SADC), would hand over the bases Saturday.
</P>
