investigate the existence of the alleged combat group that is
illegally using Malacanang's name -- the Malacanang Native Combat
Force," Barican said.
</P>
<P>
"If this group is really in existence, the president directed
Gen. (Joselin) Nazareno to neutralize it, disarm and arrest the
members, and file the appropriate charges in court," Barican said.
 
