<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary at 0800 GMT, October 28 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
VIENNA -- Visiting Russian Prime Minister Yevgeny Primakov said
here Tuesday that Russia will close the distance with the European
