<TEXT>
<P>
SHENYANG, October 28 (Xinhua) -- A Canadian industrial park
will soon be established in the city of Anshan in northeast
China's Liaoning Province, according to a recent agreement with a
Canadian delegation of entrepreneurs.
</P>
<P>
